title: EverMoon Launches Fiat Gateway with Flooz XYZ for Easy Token Purchases
description:
In an announcement made on June 13, EverMoon, a blockchain-based decentralized platform, revealed its partnership with Flooz XYZ, a Web3 infrastructure. The collaboration brings an exciting development for crypto enthusiasts, as it enables users to purchase EverMoon’s native token, EVERMOON, directly with fiat currencies on the platform’s website using Moonpay.
